snippet.title: Yu-No: A girl who chants love at the bound of this world. - Character Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
YU-NO: A girl who chants love at the bound of this world launches for the PlayStation 4 on October 1, 2019! Tread across parallel worlds to unravel a hidden mystery in this famous adventure game!

Visit the official site for more info: http://www.spike-chunsoft.com/YU-NO/

Rated Mature: Blood, Partial Nudity, Sexual Content, Strong Language, Violence
